Once there was a couple, (their name have been chiseled away), that created a powerful relic. This relic had the power of moving nations and ultimately humanity's feelings to their best intentions. All the sins of humanity, suddenly banished. For a century, the World prospered, but at a cost. People started to worship the relic as the supreme God creation.

The reality is that the relic shifted the balance created by God. Death itself got personally involved when the amount of people dying drastically reduced. There was an imbalance after all. In an attempt to restore the balance, Death destroyed the relic in parts, but unable to completely obliterate it, it put the parts away from them. Humanity was then trapped in two distinct realities: one in which love and compassion was part of it, and another where all the sins brought despair. War came back, together with the bombs and the ability of obliterating billions in a second. What remains is this tombstone, a reminder that humanity can still be saved, the balance restored.
I can't believe it. Humanity was casted away because some God didn't have the power to restore balance?
Is it you that will bring back the balance?
